You can’t make derived works and release or sell the source files as part of a content pack unless stated elsewhere in this agreement, such as the terrain of showcase demo level to present your content pack’s models.
You can make derived files and release or sell them as part of a game/virtual world/simulation.
You don’t own the content. The products are only licensed to you, they are not sold to you. All content is still copyrighted and owned by TorqueTerrains.Com and its partnering authors (unless stated otherwise within the relevant pack).
